List of changes that change behaviours of the library in a significant way (across minor releases)
and also changes that outright break backwards compatibility of the API (across mayor releases).

Bulletpoints:

    [+] Addition
    [*] Modification
    [-] Removal

====================================================================================================

v1.1.0
------
[*] Signing of documents (one or all signodes within) now checks whether a signode is aready signed
    or not. Before it silently double signed. The new behaviour is to throw an exception on
    `sign_document`, and to only sign still unsigned documents on `sign_document_all`
